'''圖廳大道站'''（{{lang-en|Tooting Broadway tube station}}）是[[倫敦地鐵|倫敦地鐵]]的一個車站，位於[[南倫敦|南倫敦]][[旺茲沃思區|旺茲沃思區]][[圖廳|圖廳]]，圖廳高街和米查姆站的路口<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com.my/maps/place/Tooting+Broadway/@51.4265597,-0.1723197,15z/data=!4m5!1m2!2m1!1stooting+broadway+underground+station!3m1!1s0x4876060bb7e7b1bd:0x10547430c94f3b4c |title=Google Maps - Tooting Broadway Underground Station |accessdate=2016-02-29 |archive-date=2020-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110165653/https://www.google.com.my/maps/place/Tooting+Broadway/@51.4265597,-0.1723197,15z/data=!4m5!1m2!2m1!1stooting+broadway+underground+station!3m1!1s0x4876060bb7e7b1bd:0x10547430c94f3b4c |dead-url=no }}</ref>。圖廳大道站是[[北線|北線]]的車站，位於倫敦第3收費區<ref>{{cite map/Standard Tube Map}}</ref>。車站開通於1926年9月13日<ref name="day">{{cite book |last=Day |first= John R |last2=Reed |first2=John |origyear=1963 |year=2010 |edition=11th |title=The Story of London's Underground |publisher=Capital Transport |p=96 |isbn=978-1-85414-341-9}}</ref>。 
